{"tid":2447650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"具惠善自稱演員非正職 拍一套《花樣男子》夠錢使逾10年","createTime":"2021-03-15T10:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:57:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60ea44d04a163ed6d06cd75ffbd4412d3585707c","tid":2447650,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PU-K1h-HxupwqUT-8zYifJM-810=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WJL4JIE2QZFVRAZ42LIWJGL3JI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPU-K1h-HxupwqUT-8zYifJM-810%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWJL4JIE2QZFVRAZ42LIWJGL3JI.jpg&h=c04481ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國36歲女星具惠善去年7月與33歲男星安宰賢辦妥離婚後，早前自爆有新戀情，展開新生活的她不時公開談及戀情，表現風騷。今日具惠善現身電台節目《朴明秀的radio show》時，亦再次提到現時的感情狀況及收入。<br />\n<br />\n一年工作一個月<br />\n具惠善於節目上表示，演員是其副業，實際上她是在搞綜合藝術，主要職業是畫家、作曲家，現時仍正在寫作中。 朴明秀問到具惠善一個月的收入時，具惠善表示：「如果工作一個月，我就可以一年做自己想做的事。」朴明秀問：「一年只工作一個月嗎？」具惠善坦言：「到現時為止，用《花樣男子》（2009年播出）賺的錢支撐到現在，現在該工作了。」<br />\n<br />\n認有曖昧對象<br />\n具惠善亦提到感情狀況，解釋現時還未正式戀愛，不過有曖昧對象，坦言都擔心不太順利，因此正在小心翼翼地努力中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MzYX92ZzdN_5xtwdrBCC6jTe_Q8=/802x661/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VYODNYCVXVBRLLCPB4H522Z4LU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMzYX92ZzdN_5xtwdrBCC6jTe_Q8%3D%2F802x661%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVYODNYCVXVBRLLCPB4H522Z4LU.png&h=62ac96bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/crJd2yzYonvbuCWUGLcxgtbLKo8=/802x1210/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UMYK52WWHNB6DONE2Z6NXCAGLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcrJd2yzYonvbuCWUGLcxgtbLKo8%3D%2F802x1210%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUMYK52WWHNB6DONE2Z6NXCAGLI.jpg&h=8be547e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GKsMsZ-oqXoOhk3LUKtcDfqyvhE=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TESEZL7SRFC6XKSNLWKVFZUWL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGKsMsZ-oqXoOhk3LUKtcDfqyvhE%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTESEZL7SRFC6XKSNLWKVFZUWL4.jpg&h=46a8f708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210315/K752EBDJJJETBCOHPTH5KUPQ2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210315%2FK752EBDJJJETBCOHPTH5KUPQ2Q%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=cd73ac56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210315%2FK752EBDJJJETBCOHPTH5KUPQ2Q%2F&h=7435fa30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210315/K752EBDJJJETBCOHPTH5KUPQ2Q/</a>"},{"pid":"02f57b4a114223740ae1505c67ac3ffcc50d5268","tid":2447650,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"癲婆...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2604699294d9a4ba8bcd3308104c8e8c5fe9d1f0","tid":2447650,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f57b4a114223740ae1505c67ac3ffcc50d5268","tid":2447650,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"癲婆...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"殺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji